ng kỳ 3 - 秋晚靈雲寺鍾樓閒望其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-Huy-B%C3%ADch/author-IUtlhs85uNhJ4NvGicsgMg">Bùi Huy Bích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/T%C3%B2ng-T%C3%A2y-Am-T%C3%B4n-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-Cao-Ly/poem-qOiN_thr8DNrp48bASUu1w">Tòng Tây Am Tôn tiên sinh xuất sứ Cao Ly - 從西庵孫先生出使高麗</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Trinh/author-HrCILDC9soRz0JVGAcDF9w">Lê Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/T%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BA%A1i/poem-B7Zr6xFz8-x_zME0mTvibg">Tự tại - 自在</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-huynh-d%E1%BB%AF-U%C3%BD-Chi-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%E1%BB%8Fng-ki%E1%BA%BFn-chi%C3%AAu-ti%E1%BB%83u-%E1%BA%A9m-th%C3%AC-d%C6%B0-d%C4%A9-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-vong-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-W7SsPhc6WPfy8fWx-G66aw">Vương thập nhị huynh dữ Uý Chi viên ngoại tương phỏng, kiến chiêu tiểu ẩm, thì dư dĩ điệu vong nhật cận, bất khứ, nhân ký - 王十二兄與畏之員外相訪，見招小飲，時予以悼亡日近，不去，因寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Y%C3%AAn-T%E1%BB%AD-s%C6%A1n-am-c%C6%B0/poem-F9xkd5q0BkCdZSjYwwQGOQ">Yên Tử sơn am cư - 安子山庵居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-ky6a-6Hq9AEiujrHK0DNTQ">Huyền Quang thiền sư</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
